The water's nice.
水很舒服。

59
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:36,240
That's right.
没错。

60
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:40,180
Or maybe you just got back from the gym and you're going to jump in the shower really
或者你刚从健身房回来，你要很快地冲个澡

61
00:02:40,180 --> 00:02:42,240
quick and before you go out again.
然后再出门。

62
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:47,360
You're not actually going to jump like you jump the action, but you're going to get into
你实际上不会像动作那样跳，但你会很快地进入

63
00:02:47,360 --> 00:02:49,080
the shower very quickly.
淋浴间。

64
00:02:49,080 --> 00:02:50,080
That's right.
没错。

65
00:02:50,080 --> 00:02:55,840
And of course, Melissa tells Michelle to jump in the cab quickly because it's pouring out
当然，Melissa告诉Michelle快上出租车，因为外面下着倾盆大雨

66
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:56,920
there.
。

67
00:02:56,920 --> 00:02:57,920
It's pouring.
下着倾盆大雨。

68
00:02:57,920 --> 00:02:58,920
