00:02:58,920 --> 00:02:59,920
The rain.
雨。

70
00:02:59,920 --> 00:03:02,000
Pouring water, pouring wine.
倒水，倒酒。

71
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:03,000
That's right.
没错。

72
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:05,160
It's actually, yeah, it's pouring water out there.
实际上，是的，外面在下倾盆大雨。

73
00:03:05,160 --> 00:03:07,600
It means it's raining very, very hard.
意思是雨下得非常大。

74
00:03:07,600 --> 00:03:11,480
Okay, so it's not just drizzling a little, little bit.
好的，所以不只是下点毛毛雨。

75
00:03:11,480 --> 00:03:12,760
It's raining very hard.
雨下得很大。

76
00:03:12,760 --> 00:03:14,040
It's pouring rain.
下着倾盆大雨。

77
00:03:14,040 --> 00:03:15,960
Okay, so we don't have to say the word rain.
好的，所以我们不必说“rain”这个词。

78
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:17,640
We can just say it's pouring.
我们可以只说“it's pouring”。

79
00:03:17,640 --> 00:03:18,640
That's right.
没错。

80
00:03:18,640 --> 00:03:23,320
As you can see in that sentence, Melissa doesn't say at any time it's raining, but we understand
正如你在那句话中看到的，Melissa任何时候都没说下雨，但我们明白。

81
00:03:23,320 --> 00:03:28,520
that when somebody says it's pouring out there, you know that it means it's raining very hard.
当有人说“外面下着倾盆大雨”时，你就知道那意味着雨下得很大。

82
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:29,520
Can't be chocolate.
不可能是巧克力。

83
00:03:29,520 --> 00:03:32,160
Can't be chocolate, can't be dogs or cats, right?
不可能是巧克力，也不可能是狗或猫，对吧？

84
00:03:32,160 --> 00:03:33,160
No.
不是。

85
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:39,400
All right, so Michelle gets in the cab and she says, well, we have to pick up Mr. Campbell.
好的，所以米歇尔上了出租车，她说，嗯，我们得去接坎贝尔先生。

86
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:43,320
And Melissa says, yep, we need to pick him up at the hotel.
梅丽莎说，是的，我们需要去酒店接他。

87
00:03:43,320 --> 00:03:46,160
All right, the verb here is to pick up.
好的，这里的动词是“pick up”。

88
00:03:46,160 --> 00:03:49,640
Now we want to just remember this as a phrasal verb.
现在我们想把它记住为一个短语动词。

89
00:03:49,640 --> 00:03:54,560
You pick someone up in your car, you could even pick someone up on your bicycle.
你可以开车接某人，甚至可以用自行车接某人。

90
00:03:54,560 --> 00:03:55,560
That's right, that's right.
没错，没错。

91
00:03:55,560 --> 00:04:02,160
So, but you can see that you can say we need to pick up Tommy at the hotel or you can say
所以，但你可以看到，你可以说“我们需要去酒店接汤米”，或者你可以说

92
00:04:02,160 --> 00:04:04,060
