或者你能去干洗店取衣服吗？

98
00:04:15,320 --> 00:04:16,320
That's right.
没错。

99
00:04:16,320 --> 00:04:17,680
It means to go collect something.
意思是去取某物。

100
00:04:17,680 --> 00:04:18,680
That's right.
没错。

101
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:20,280
So you can use it in different ways.
所以你可以用不同的方式使用它。

102
00:04:20,280 --> 00:04:24,760
You can put the noun in between pick up or you can put it after.
你可以把名词放在“pick up”中间，或者放在后面。

103
00:04:24,760 --> 00:04:27,400
And all right, so they're going to go pick up Mr. Campbell.
好的，所以他们要去接坎贝尔先生。

104
00:04:27,400 --> 00:04:30,040
Now they're talking, well, they're kind of gossiping a little bit.
现在他们在聊天，嗯，他们有点八卦。

105
