Actually, we need to pick him up at his hotel and then go to the conference.
实际上，我们需要去他的酒店接他，然后去参加会议。

139
00:06:10,880 --> 00:06:12,240
Oh, I see.
哦，我明白了。

140
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:13,240
