好的。

141
00:06:13,240 --> 00:06:14,760
So I heard you got married.
所以我听说你结婚了。

142
00:06:14,760 --> 00:06:15,760
Congratulations.
恭喜。

143
00:06:15,760 --> 00:06:17,120
Oh, thank you.
哦，谢谢。

144
00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:18,720
I'm very excited.
我非常兴奋。

145
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:23,200
We were going to get married next year, but then we decided to get married on holiday
我们本来打算明年结婚，但后来决定在假期结婚

