00:06:53,080 --> 00:06:55,200
So now we're back with part two of Fluency Builder.
现在我们回到流利度构建的第二部分。

161
00:06:55,200 --> 00:06:58,880
Let's get started with the first phrase.
让我们从第一个短语开始。

162
00:06:58,880 --> 00:07:03,000
When she says that they got married on holiday, what does that mean?
当她说他们在度假时结婚，那是什么意思？

163
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:05,480
On holiday is another way of saying on vacation.
"On holiday" 是"on vacation"的另一种说法。

164
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:10,520
So while we were having a holiday somewhere, this happened.
所以，当我们在某个地方度假时，这件事发生了。

165
00:07:10,520 --> 00:07:14,480
